trans-unit.source: Enumerates the contents of a binary tree.

**NuGet package**: <see href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/System.Collections.Immutable/">System.Collections.Immutable</see> (<see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.immutable?#Remarks">about immutable collections and how to install</see>)
trans-unit.target: **NuGet package**: <see href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/System.Collections.Immutable/">System.Collections.Immutable</see>（<see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.immutable?#Remarks">关于不可变集合和安装方法</see>）

trans-unit.source: This structure should be kept synchronized with the other two binary tree enumerators: <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableList%601.Enumerator?displayProperty=nameWithType> and <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableSortedSet%601.Enumerator?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: 此结构应保持与其他两个二进制树枚举器同步：<xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableList%601.Enumerator?displayProperty=nameWithType>和<xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableSortedSet%601.Enumerator?displayProperty=nameWithType>。

trans-unit.source: When this enumerator is used as a value type (that is, when it isn't boxed), do not copy it by assigning it to a second variable or by passing it to another method.
trans-unit.target: 此枚举器用作值类型 （即，当它不进行了装箱），不要复制它通过将其分配给第二个变量，或将其传递到另一种方法。

trans-unit.source: When this enumerator is disposed of, it returns a mutable reference type stack to a resource pool, and if the value type enumerator is copied (which can easily happen unintentionally if you pass the value around), there is a risk that a stack that has already been returned to the resource pool may still be in use by one of the enumerator copies, leading to data corruption or exceptions.
trans-unit.target: 在此枚举器释放的时，它将返回可变的引用类型堆栈给资源池，并且如果值类型枚举器复制 （这种轻松情况无意中，如果通过周围的值），则存在的风险，已经过堆栈返回到资源池可能仍将使用的一个枚举器副本，从而导致数据损坏或异常。

trans-unit.source: Gets the element at the current position of the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 获取枚举数当前位置的元素。

trans-unit.source: The element at the current position of the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 位于枚举器当前位置的元素。

trans-unit.source: Releases the resources used by the current instance of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableSortedDictionary`2.Enumerator" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 释放 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableSortedDictionary`2.Enumerator" /> 类的当前实例使用的资源。

trans-unit.source: Advances the enumerator to the next element of the immutable sorted dictionary.
trans-unit.target: 将枚举器推进到不可变排序字典的下一个元素。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the enumerator was successfully advanced to the next element; <see langword="false" /> if the enumerator has passed the end of the sorted dictionary.
trans-unit.target: 如果枚举器已成功地推进到下一个元素，则为 <see langword="true" />；如果枚举器已传递到排序字典的末尾，则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Sets the enumerator to its initial position, which is before the first element in the immutable sorted dictionary.
trans-unit.target: 将枚举器设置到其初始位置，该位置位于不可变排序字典中的第一个元素之前。
